\displaystyle \frac{\sum_{r=0}^{24}\binom{100}{r}.\binom{100}{4r+2}}{\sum_{r=1}^{25}\binom{200}{8r-6}}= 
\displaystyle \sum_{r=0}^{24}\binom{100}{r}.\binom{100}{4r+2} = \binom{100}{0}.\binom{100}{2}+\binom{100}{1}.\binom{100}{6}+\binom{100}{2}.\binom{100}{10}+......+\binom{100}{24}.\binom{100}{98}
\displaystyle \sum_{r=1}^{25}\binom{200}{8r-6} = \binom{200}{2}+\binom{200}{10}+\binom{200}{18}+.........+\binom{200}{194}
